snippet.title: Meet Kapil Sharma | Episode 90
snippet.description:
Watch the trailer of Kapil Sharma movie at:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xtd1aB-iLe0&t=52s

Sandeep Maheshwari is a name among millions who struggled, failed and surged ahead in search of success, happiness and contentment. Just like any middle class guy, he too had a bunch of unclear dreams and a blurred vision of his goals in life. All he had was an undying learning attitude to hold on to. Rowing through ups and downs, it was time that taught him the true meaning of his life.

To know more, log on to www.sandeepmaheshwari.com

#kapilsharma #sandeepmaheshwari

snippet.title: Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Bhoot Bungalow || MCM
snippet.description:
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu Bhoot Bungalow MCM

In this new episode of Middle Class Madhu, Madhu and his buddies decide to film a horror movie at an abandoned house in hopes of boosting the success of his YouTube video. In order to make the film more realistic, they start acting as they enter the ancient bungalow to shoot some scary footage. See the entire brand-new episode of Booth Bungalow to find what happened next.

Tere Bin Episode 25 Teaser - 16th March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

snippet.title: Oscars: RRR's Naatu Naatu Honored With EPIC Performance
snippet.description: Rahul Sipligunj and Kaala Bhairava sing their 'RRR' song, 'Naatu Naatu,' in an epic dance number at the 95th Academy Awards. The movie later makes history as it becomes the first Indian feature film to win an Oscar, with the track's composer and lyricist, M.M. Keeravaani and Chandrabose, nabbing Best Original Song. The 2023 Oscars aired on ABC.

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

snippet.description:

Tere Bin Episode 24 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 16th March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3720 - 16 Mar 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3720: Baccho Ka Secret Project
--------------------------------------------------------
At the soda, the Gokuldham men discuss Tapu Sena and their recent activities. Tapu Sena secretly plans to do something to surprise their parents, so they secretly meet at a studio. Jetha asks Taarak about Tapu Sena's plan of action, but Taarak has also failed to retrieve any information. So the Gokuldham men decide to ask Chmpaklal to intervene because he has a good rapport with the kids. When Tapu informs Bhide that Sonu will reach home a bit late, Bhide gets worried and calls the other men; they decide to uncover their secret mission anyhow. Will Tapu Sena's mission be unveiled finally?

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3720, 16 Mar 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3719 - 15 Mar 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3719: Tapu Sena's New Mission
--------------------------------------------------------
The parents are worried for their kids' future. They catch them hanging out at the clubhouse and ask them questions. They are worried that the Tapu Sena is not serious about their lives and careers. Tapu Sena tries to make them understand. Taarak decides to have a talk with them without the parents. He makes them understand their parents' point of view as well. Tapu Sena decided and promises that they will think of something. They discuss it amongst themselves and try to come up with a solution. 

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3719, 15 Mar 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Former corporator from Dahisar Sheetal Mhatre lashed out at Uddhav Thackeray faction after an objectionable video, allegedly morphed, showing Shiv Sena MLA Prakash Surve with her went viral on social media. The video zooms in on Surve and Mhatre as the two join CM Eknath Shinde's cavalcade. Mhatre marched to Dahisar police station in the wee hours of Sunday to lodge a complaint against the miscreants. The police have arrested two persons in connection with the case. Mhatre released a video and said," When your opponents have nothing left to target you with, they stoop to such cheap tactics. Targeting a woman who is someone's mother, daughter, wife with a video like this is disturbing. Everyone knows who is behind this. It's shocking that something like this can be peddled to malign, defame us. Those who are behind this have no ground to stand on and that's why they are stopping to this level."

#uddhavthackeray #mumbai #latestnews

snippet.title: How HEATWAVES are destroying Indian economy | Analysis by Abhi and Niyu
snippet.description:
In this video, Abhi and Niyu discuss the economic impact of heatwaves on India.

In February and March 2023, temperatures in many parts of the country have crossed 40 degree Celsius. This means we have a hot summer ahead. A hot summer means impact on agriculture and as a result on the Indian economy.

#indianeconomy #finance #abhiandniyu  

What is a heatwave?

A heatwave in the Indian context refers to an extended period of abnormally high temperatures that occur during the summer months, typically from March to June. Heatwaves in India are often characterized by temperatures exceeding 40¬∞C and are associated with high levels of humidity, making them particularly dangerous for human health. They can also lead to crop failures, water shortages, and power outages, among other problems. In recent years, heatwaves in India have become more frequent and intense, likely due to climate change and urbanization.

How does a heatwave impact India?

Heatwaves can have a significant impact on India in several ways. First and foremost, they pose a serious threat to human health, with the elderly, children, and those with pre-existing medical conditions being particularly vulnerable. Heat-related illnesses such as heat exhaustion, heat stroke, and dehydration can lead to hospitalization and even death. Additionally, heatwaves can exacerbate water scarcity issues in India, as water sources dry up and demand for water increases. They can also cause power outages as the demand for electricity rises, further compounding the impact on human health and well-being. Finally, heatwaves can have a detrimental effect on agriculture, with crops being destroyed or failing to produce due to the extreme heat and lack of water.

A video by Abhiraj Rajadhyaksha & Niyati Mavinkurve

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3718 - 14 Mar 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3718: Baccho Ka Bhavishya
--------------------------------------------------------
When Tapu Sena meets at the clubhouse, they discuss their parents' concerns about their future. Tapu suggests to his friends that they somehow have to prove themselves and make their parents proud. Later, the ladies of Gokuldham also discussed the same topic. Dr. Hathi's wife tells Madhavi to ask Bhide to make the kids understand about being diligent. As the Gokuldham women enjoy their badminton game, Jetha intervenes and accepts Babita's challenge. At the soda shop, when Iyer gets sleepy, Jetha deliberately spills soda on his face. Watch the full episode to enjoy the upcoming funny happenings!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3718, 14 Mar 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Oscars 2023: RRR's Naatu Naatu wins best original song
The song Naatu Naatu from the hit Telugu-language film RRR has made history by becoming the first Indian film song to win an Oscar.

The blockbuster track won Best Original Song at the 95th Academy Awards, beating heavyweights like Lady Gaga and Rihanna.

Its catchy tempo and choreography has captivated audiences around the world.

India won a second Oscar for The Elephant Whisperers which won in the Best Documentary Short film category.

The documentary, which tells the story of a couple who care for an injured baby elephant after it gets separated from its herd, is the first Indian production to win in this category.
https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-india-64935389
